            "wrapper": {
                "width": "",
                "class": "",
                "id": ""
            },
            "message": "<strong>Filters tab<\/strong>\r\nThese filters are a direct relation to the dropdown filters on the \/jobs page. Setting them will make this job appear when sorted by the respective category.\r\n\r\n<strong>+ tab<\/strong>\r\nIf a selection is not available click the '+' tab and enter the name of the selection in the related 'Add' box and 'update' the job. Your addition will be added and selected as a new option in the related dropdown.\r\n\r\n<strong>Nt: Removing options and Salary scales<\/strong>\r\nFor advanced editing including adding a Salary scales navigate to the Jobs > Jobs Category link on the admin bar. Please be aware this is for advanced users only and has site wide ramifications, contact support if you are unsure what to do.",
